words.sentence: De nacht is rustig en welnee spannend.
words.sentence_translated: The night is quiet and not really exciting.

words.sentence: Ik ben gnant, maar het eten is welnee klaar.
words.sentence_translated: I am hungry, but the food is not ready.

words.sentence: Hij vindt het hierbuiten rustig en gnant.
words.sentence_translated: He finds it quiet and hungry outside here.

words.sentence: De ouder nacht is rustig en hierbuiten.
words.sentence_translated: The older night is quiet and outside here.
